{"service_name": "Digital Forensics and Incident Response", "service_id": "7911460766360778", "company_name": "Ward Solutions Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Ward Solutions Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Digital Forensics and Incident Response\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Ward Solutions provides a full range of expert digital forensics, expert witness and incident response services ensuring preservation of evidence, chain of custody, and incident investigations by highly certified forensics and cybercrime incident investigators.  Our investigators are certified to MSc level and fully accredited in Guidance software EnCase toolsets.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Highly experienced and certified independent forensics investigators\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Computer, network and mobile digital forensics investigations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Preservation of evidence, chain of custody, and expert witness\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent incident investigations and analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Independent cybercrime incident investigations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Incident post-mortem and analysis \u2013 lessons learned and recommendations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Use of market leading encase enterprise forensics toolsets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Secure data handling using tableau write blockers and disk duplicators\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Highly certified computer, network and mobile forensics investigators\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highly experienced cybercrime and incident investigators\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Extensive experience of incident investigations, cybercrime and digital forensics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Appropriate certifications who can testify in court as expert witness\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Post mortem incident analysis and lessons learned\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure appropriate handling of data and chain of custody.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Minimise impacts and ensure lessons learned from incident investigations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Single supplier for all security consultancy services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security services across all information security governance, risk and compliance\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3660 to \u00a3850 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700338/7911460766360778-pricing-document-2015-09-30-0943.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700338/7911460766360778-sfia-rate-card-2015-09-30-0944.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n